; --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
; @Title: FreeRTOS Demo for TRACE32 OS Awareness
; @Description: 
;   
;   This batchfile loads all necessary files to demonstrate
;   the OS Awareness for FreeRTOS.
;   
; @Keywords: awareness, RTOS, FreeRTOS
